                            <comment id="17369" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 7 Jul 2011 08:07:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This bug has been fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-386&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite replay-single&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-386&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-386&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. This tick needs to be closed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14324" author="brian" created="Fri, 13 May 2011 08:47:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This sounds like addressing the symptom and not the problem though.  Should adding &quot;+option&quot; to a debug mask that is already including everything really cause some sort of failure?  It seems to be that it should be a NOOP, yes?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
